extendedInfo.description: Guess the Cities Logo Pop QuizAll those fascinating cities in the world. All the variety of people, cultures and languages. Can you name all the capitals on the planet? Do you know where Warsaw is? Is "London" ringing any bells? And how about Paris, Berlin or Moscow? Play now the fascinating and one and only Guess the Cities Logo Pop Quiz, where you will be tested to the edge of your possibilities. Check out now if you know all the capitals in the world. Check up your score on world leaderboard and invite your friends to come over and play on one screen with 4 people at the same time! Download Guess the Cities Logo Pop Quiz, while it's FREE!Guess the Cities Logo Pop Quiz
